<style>
  .product_faq {
    background: #3C1F1B;
  }
  .product_faq-wrapper {
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 50px;
  }
  .product_faq-text {
    width: 515px;
  }
  .product_faq-text h2, .product_faq-text p {
    color: #F2F2EA;
  }
  .product_faq-text p {
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .product_faq-items {
    width: calc(100% - 565px);
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .product_faq-item {
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #fff;
    transition: 0.3s;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 4px 40px;
  }
  .product_faq-item:hover {
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .product_faq-item-title {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 16px 0px;
  }
  .product_faq-item-title p {
    max-width: calc(100% - 38px);
  }
  a.product_faq-item-cross {
    display: block;
    height: max-content;
  }
  .product_faq-item-title a svg {
      height: 28px;
      width: auto;
      transition: .3s;
      transform: rotate(0deg);
    display: block;
  }
  .product_faq-item-title a svg path {
    transition: .3s;
  }
  .product_faq-item.active .product_faq-item-title a svg {
      transform: rotate(45deg);
  }
  .product_faq-item.active .product_faq-item-title a svg path {
    stroke: #F24F14;
  }
  .product_faq-item-text {
    height: max-content;
    max-height: 0px;
    overflow: hidden;
    width: 100%;
    transition: .5s;
    position: relative;
  }
  .product_faq-item-text a {
    text-decoration: underline;
    transition: .3s;
  }
  .product_faq-item-text a:hover {
    opacity: .85;
  }
  .product_faq-item-text a:active {
    opacity: .7;
  }
  .product_faq-item.active .product_faq-item-text {
    padding-top: 21px;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    max-height: 300px;
  }
  .product_faq-item-text::before {
    content:'';
    display: block;
    height: 100%;
    max-height: 0px;
    width: 100%;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0px;
    left: 0;
    background: rgba(60, 31, 27, 0.30);
    transition: .5s;
  }
  .product_faq-item-text::before {
    max-height: 1px;
  }
  .product_faq-desc {
    margin-top: 15px;
  }
  .product_faq-btns {
    margin-top: 30px;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .product_faq-btns a {
    margin: 0;
  }
  .product_faq-a {
    text-decoration: underline;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .product_faq-btns-desktop-hidden {
    display: none;
  }
  @media(max-width: 1450px) {
    .product_faq-item {
        padding: 4px 30px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 1250px) {
    .product_faq-btns-mobile-hidden {
      display: none;
    }
    .product_faq-btns-desktop-hidden {
      display: flex!important;
    }
    .product_faq-items {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .product_faq-btns {
      margin-top: 0;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .product_faq-text {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .product_faq-wrapper {
      gap: 40px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 750px) {
    .product_faq {
      padding: 60px 0;
    }
    .product_faq-wrapper a.rebranding_btn {
      margin: 0px auto;
    }
    .product_faq-item-title {
      padding: 15px 0;
    }
    .product_faq-item {
        padding: 0px 20px;
    }
    .product_faq-item.active .product_faq-item-text {
    padding-top: 15px;
    padding-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .product_faq-item-title a svg {
      height: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="container rebranding_container">
  <div class="product_faq-wrapper block-flex-wrap">
    <div class="product_faq-text">
      <h2 class="h2-heading-ss">
        Featured
        <span class="h2-heading-pp">questions</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="product_faq-desc body-text">
        Have more questions? Visit our <a href="https://legitgrails.frontkb.com/en" target="_blank" class="product_faq-a standart-hover">Help Center</a>
      </p>
      <div class="product_faq-btns block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 product_faq-btns-mobile-hidden">
        <a href="https://legitgrails.frontkb.com/en" target="_blank" class="rebranding_btn">
        Help Center
      </a>
        <a href="#product_boxes" class="rebranding_btn rebranding_btn-main product_authenticate-now-btn-track">
        Authenticate now
      </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="product_faq-items block-flex-wrap">
      <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">How Does LegitGrails’ Authentication Process Work?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            LegitGrails combines artificial intelligence with expert human analysis to verify the authenticity of your Cartier items. The process begins when you upload clear images of your product. Our AI system analyzes the photos against a detailed database of Cartier designs and features. 
<br><br>
After the AI scan, our experienced authenticators carefully examine the images, using their deep knowledge of Cartier’s craftsmanship and design standards to confirm authenticity. We’ll ensure the process remains accurate and efficient if more information is needed.
</p>
        </div>
      </div>
              <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">How Long Does LegitGrails’ Authentication Take?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            LegitGrails’ standard authentication service provides results within 12 hours of receiving your item’s photos. For faster results, we offer an express option that delivers results within 6 hours. Our team is committed to providing accurate and timely assessments to meet your needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">Is Cartier Considered a Luxury Brand?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            Yes, Cartier is widely regarded as one of the top luxury brands in the world, known for its exquisite jewelry, watches, and accessories. Founded in 1847 in Paris, Cartier has built a reputation for elegance and sophistication, often referred to as “the jeweler of kings and the king of jewelers.” Its commitment to exceptional craftsmanship and timeless design has made it a cornerstone of the luxury market.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">Which Company Owns Cartier?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            Cartier is a subsidiary of the Swiss-based luxury conglomerate Richemont Group, which also owns several other prestigious brands. This positioning within a high-end portfolio reinforces Cartier’s status as a leader in the luxury sector.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">Is Cartier a Better Brand Than Rolex?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            Both Cartier and Rolex are highly respected luxury brands with distinct identities. Cartier is known for its elegant, jewelry-inspired watch designs and use of precious metals and gemstones. 
<br><br>
Rolex, by contrast, is celebrated for its precision engineering, durability, and iconic sports watches. Whether you value Cartier’s refined elegance or Rolex’s technical mastery, which brand is better comes down to personal preference.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">Is Cartier Manufactured in Switzerland?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            Cartier’s watches are primarily manufactured in Switzerland, particularly in La Chaux-de-Fonds and Geneva. These locations are renowned for their watchmaking expertise, ensuring that Cartier timepieces meet the highest standards of Swiss craftsmanship.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
              <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">Which Celebrities and Public Figures Wear Cartier?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            Cartier’s timeless designs have attracted many celebrities and public figures. Taylor Swift recently wore a Cartier Santos Demoiselle watch at the 2025 iHeartRadio Music Awards. Many other high-profile personalities, including royalty and Hollywood stars, have worn Cartier pieces, reinforcing the brand’s status and appeal.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">Does Cartier Use Real Gold in Its Products?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            Cartier uses genuine precious metals, including 18k gold and platinum, in its jewelry and watch designs. The brand’s commitment to quality ensures that all materials are authentic and of the highest standard.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
      <div class="product_faq-btns block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 product_faq-btns-desktop-hidden">
        <a href="https://legitgrails.frontkb.com/en" target="_blank" class="rebranding_btn">
        Help Center
      </a>
        <a href="#product_boxes" class="rebranding_btn rebranding_btn-main product_authenticate-now-btn-track">
        Authenticate now
      </a>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>

